Package org.vngx.jsch.util

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    HostKeyRepository
    An interface for defining a repository which manages and validates host keys from the local file system.
    Logger
    Interface for defining a simple logger for the SSH library to reduce any external dependencies which would be required for logging libraries such as log4j, slf4j, et al.
    SocketFactory
    Interface for defining a factory which creates Sockets to a given host and port and supplies methods for retrieving input and output streams to read and write to open sockets.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DataUtil
    Static utility class providing some general data manipulation methods.
    HostKey
    Host key implementation as outlined in the RFC4251 spec for SSH.
    KeyPair
    Abstract implementation of a key pair.
    KeyPairDSA
    Implementation of KeyPair for generating a public/private key pair using DSA encryption.
    KeyPairRSA
    Implementation of KeyPair for generating a public/private key pair using RSA encryption.
    KnownHosts
    Implementation of HostKeyRepository for registering and checking host keys on the local system.
    SocketFactory.DefaultSocketFactory
    Default implementation of SocketFactory for creating a socket connection to a host/port with or without a timeout.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    HostKeyRepository.Check
    Enum constants for the available results which can be returned when checking repository for host key.
    KeyType
    Enum constant to represent the different types of host keys.
    Logger.Level
    Enum constants for logging levels.
